headline.main: Trump Win Probably Didn’t Cause Canadian Immigration Website’s Crash
headline.print_headline: Trump Win Probably Didn’t Cause Canadian Immigration Website’s Crash

lead_paragraph: Technology entrepreneur Greg Gianforte says he has commitments from enough delegates to secure the Republican nomination for Ryan Zinke's former seat in the U.S. House, but another Montana contender said Thursday he doesn't believe Gianforte has the votes locked down.
